Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.70,0:00:02.74,Dinamik,,0,0,0,,Hello, friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.76,0:00:06.16,Dinamik,,0,0,0,,Hello, hello, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.90,0:00:08.59,Dinamik,,0,0,0,,Şükran, you who understand polytheism, let me take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.98,0:00:09.50,Dinamik,,0,0,0,,All right, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.14,0:00:11.74,Dinamik,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.32,0:00:14.22,Dinamik,,0,0,0,,"No, we're not counting; not even a drop of water—we're not."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.69,0:00:16.00,Dinamik,,0,0,0,,There's a pair of pants there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.33,0:00:17.82,Dinamik,,0,0,0,,The water is yours now—congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.33,0:00:21.10,Dinamik,,0,0,0,,We have nothing to do with the water; it’s because of my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.44,0:00:22.03,Dinamik,,0,0,0,,Do you mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.98,0:00:23.92,Dinamik,,0,0,0,,So, do I belong here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.23,0:00:24.89,Dinamik,,0,0,0,,The foreigner said.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.89,0:00:27.33,Dinamik,,0,0,0,,What a mess I’ve made.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.66,0:00:28.73,Dinamik,,0,0,0,,You saw us in the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.16,0:00:30.14,Dinamik,,0,0,0,,Did you think there was a gardener?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.66,0:00:31.96,Dinamik,,0,0,0,,I am Özgür, my driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.52,0:00:33.60,Dinamik,,0,0,0,,Arif. Arif.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.82,0:00:36.71,Dinamik,,0,0,0,,I’m also the world-class boxing champion, as you all know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.00,0:00:37.56,Dinamik,,0,0,0,,It's a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.85,0:00:38.06,Dinamik,,0,0,0,,He is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.03,0:00:39.97,Dinamik,,0,0,0,,That's when you get down to business.
